#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn56.10"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.10:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Samādhivagga "
msgstr "1. Immersion "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 10. Tiracchānakathāsutta → kathā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn56.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Tiracchānakathāsutta "
msgstr "10. Unworthy Talk "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.420, sc1
msgctxt "sn56.10:1.1"
msgid "“Mā, bhikkhave, anekavihitaṃ tiracchānakathaṃ katheyyātha, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr "“Mendicants, don’t engage in all kinds of unworthy talk, such as "

#. VAR: janapadakathaṃ itthikathaṃ → itthikathaṃ purisakathaṃ (bj, pts1, mr) | itthīkathaṃ purisakathaṃ (s1-3, km)
#. VAR: sūrakathaṃ → surākathaṃ (si, s1-3)
msgctxt "sn56.10:1.2"
msgid "rājakathaṃ corakathaṃ mahāmattakathaṃ senākathaṃ, bhayakathaṃ yuddhakathaṃ, annakathaṃ pānakathaṃ vatthakathaṃ sayanakathaṃ mālākathaṃ gandhakathaṃ, ñātikathaṃ yānakathaṃ gāmakathaṃ nigamakathaṃ nagarakathaṃ janapadakathaṃ itthikathaṃ sūrakathaṃ visikhākathaṃ kumbhaṭṭhānakathaṃ, pubbapetakathaṃ nānattakathaṃ, lokakkhāyikaṃ samuddakkhāyikaṃ itibhavābhavakathaṃ iti vā. "
msgstr "talk about kings, bandits, and ministers; talk about armies, threats, and wars; talk about food, drink, clothes, and beds; talk about garlands and fragrances; talk about family, vehicles, villages, towns, cities, and countries; talk about women and heroes; street talk and talk at the well; talk about the departed; motley talk; tales of land and sea; and talk about being reborn in this or that state of existence. "

msgctxt "sn56.10:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "sn56.10:1.4"
msgid "Nesā, bhikkhave, kathā atthasaṃhitā nādibrahmacariyakā na nibbidāya na virāgāya na nirodhāya na upasamāya na abhiññāya na sambodhāya na nibbānāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "Because those discussions aren’t beneficial or relevant to the fundamentals of the spiritual life. They don’t lead to disillusionment, dispassion, cessation, peace, insight, awakening, and extinguishment. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn56.10:2.1"
msgid "Kathentā ca kho tumhe, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti katheyyātha, ‘ayaṃ dukkhasamudayo’ti katheyyātha, ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodho’ti katheyyātha, ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti katheyyātha. "
msgstr "When you discuss, you should discuss: ‘This is suffering’ … ‘This is the origin of suffering’ … ‘This is the cessation of suffering’ … ‘This is the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering’. … "

msgctxt "sn56.10:2.2"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn56.10:2.3"
msgid "Esā, bhikkhave, kathā atthasaṃhitā, esā ādibrahmacariyakā, esā nibbidāya virāgāya nirodhāya upasamāya abhiññāya sambodhāya nibbānāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn56.10:3.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti. "
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.10:3.2"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.10:3.3"
msgid "Samādhivaggo paṭhamo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn56.10:4.1"
msgid "Samādhi paṭisallānā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.10:4.2"
msgid "kulaputtā apare duve; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.10:4.3"
msgid "Samaṇabrāhmaṇā vitakkaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn56.10:4.4"
msgid "cintā viggāhikā kathāti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
